description: Add new address and check update successfully

steps.name: Click to Address Link
Click to Add New button
Input to first name textbox with value Automation
Input to last name textbox with value FC
Input to email textbox with value automationfc.vn@gmail.com
Input to company textbox with value Automation FC
Select value in country dropdown list with value Viet Nam
Input to city textbox with value Da Nang
Input to Address 1 textbox with value 123/04 Le Lai
Input to Address 2 textbox with value 234/05 Hai Phong
Input to zip code textbox with value 550000
Input to phone number textbox with value 0123456789
Input to fax number textbox with value 0987654321
Click to Save button
Verify name (first + last name) is displayed is Automation FC
Verify email is displayed is Email: automationfc.vn@gmail.com
Verify phone number is displayed is Phone number: 0123456789
Verify fax number is displayed is Fax number: 0987654321
Verify company is displayed is Automation FC
Verify address 1 is displayed is 123/04 Le Lai
Verify address 2 is displayed is 234/05 Hai Phong
Verify city + state + zip is displayed is Da Nang, 550000
